@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kpnvlr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v2
    v0 = v2
    v0 = (0.74 / (wp.abs(tmp + 0.31) * 0.60))
    v1 = (wp.cos(0.22) - wp.abs(0.06))
    v1 = (tmp + wp.exp(wp.exp(tmp + 0.95)))
    tmp = v0
    tmp = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.60) + (v0 + 0.48 - v1 + 0.61)) + wp.cos((v2 + 0.01 - v0 + 0.48)))
    v2 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.49 * v2 + 0.27)) * v2)
    data[tid] = v0
